### Code
- Implemented the two-stage retrieval system (`retriever.py`)
  - Bi-encoder stage using `nomic-ai/nomic-embed-code` for dense code retrieval
  - Cross-encoder stage using `cross-encoder/ms-marco-MiniLM-L-12-v2` for re-ranking
  - In-memory numpy embedding store with efficient `argpartition`-based candidate selection
- Integrated two-stage retriever into the main pipeline (`main.py`) alongside the baseline

### Experiments
- Ran retrieval experiments comparing baseline (BGE-base-en-v1.5) against the two-stage system across FastAPI, Pydantic, and Requests repositories
- Generated and analyzed all result CSVs for both configurations

Added documentation in the final report 